<div class="px-6 py-16 bg-gray-100 dark:bg-neutral-950">
  <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto text-center">
    <h1 class="mb-4 text-4xl font-extrabold leading-none">Support My Work</h1>
    <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-3">
      If you enjoy my apps, there are two great ways to support me:
    </p>
    <ul class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-8 space-y-2 text-left max-w-md mx-auto">
      <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
        <span class="text-yellow-500 mt-0.5">&#9733;</span>
        <span>Leave a <strong class="text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200">5-star written review</strong> on the App Store — it goes a long way in helping others discover my apps.</span>
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
        <span class="mt-0.5">&#128176;</span>
        <span>Send a tip via Venmo to help fund future development.</span>
      </li>
    </ul>
    <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4">
      <a
        href="https://apps.apple.com/us/developer/richard-witherspoon/id1690898003"
        class="app-store-button"
      >
        &#63743 App Store
      </a>
      <a
        href="https://venmo.com/u/rspoon3"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="donate-button"
      >
        Venmo
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .app-store-button {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 15px 50px;
    border-radius: 60px;
    background-color: #f61d1d;
    color: #fff;
    font-weight: bold;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: opacity 0.3s ease;
  }

  .app-store-button:hover {
    text-decoration: none;
    color: #fff;
    opacity: 0.7;
  }

  .donate-button {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 15px 50px;
    border-radius: 60px;
    background-color: #008cff;
    color: #fff;
    font-weight: bold;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: opacity 0.3s ease;
  }

  .donate-button:hover {
    text-decoration: none;
    color: #fff;
    opacity: 0.7;
  }
</style>
